<br>
I generally use the jaspers in low end mob encounters and dots in the higher level encounters.  I almost always keep symbols up but 5GP vs 10PP for 100-150 extra HP is only worth it on the big time mobs anyway, of which you won't be killing in a regular experience group in DL.<br>
