<br>
ML is a great way to go for this.  In FFA Dreadlands situations, I would make sure I looted more of the dogs because they tended to have higher amounts of plat.  At some points, it meant not medding and slower pulling, but if the group demanded dots, it was the only way to make sure my costs were covered.<br>
<br>
It's your right to be reimbursed, on them.<br>
